{"tid":2509072,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"英國住屋問題","createTime":"2021-04-29T07:47:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T18:03:46.000Z","uid":240606,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"91070cd1ffef2c26f85cceec245e79e0449d1d5e","tid":2509072,"uid":240606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T07:47:08.000Z","msg":"我哋一家三口老婆想買定一間4房(樓花)約350萬，咁我都覺得ok. 不過佢家姐一家四口連我外父母都話要走，我老婆話佢地做唔到按揭，要6個人先住我間屋(大約住一年)，我當堂呆拿咗。屌你原本hk 400 呎3人，宜家1400 呎9人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。老婆話我自撚獅唔幫自己人，咁我角度如果我本身住緊佢哋要緊急著草的話我會比佢地住咯，宜家實況係可能半年後先收樓仲要係清水樓，根本9條友去到都要先租搵學校,宜家大把大把時間要 planing,點解要 plan 嗰西 plan?? 佢哋6個一路租唔得咩?想問大家點睇。<br />\n利身：我老婆家姐細嘅兩件好細，所以想兩老傍住"},{"pid":"c5e192b42faa7a70e45fffac97b6667a6a671058","tid":2509072,"uid":171507,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T07:55:20.000Z","msg":"佢屋企人擺明夾9你攞你地着數啦，但你老婆都開埋聲幫口就要硬食架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c09089954950fb68effe794b474781a03f619a49","tid":2509072,"uid":284855,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T07:56:41.000Z","msg":"三個家庭住埋一齊，等開片啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4075225f864fec4700ab0f04aaf88b100f4abff5","tid":2509072,"uid":289459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T07:57:21.000Z","msg":"夾鳩你拎著數, <br />\n閪女人"},{"pid":"9e2fdf5dbae5a3ed831bf7f6c3da521ed7b812af","tid":2509072,"uid":8880,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T07:58:45.000Z","msg":"叫佢地自己plan啦<br />\n要嚟住就交租"},{"pid":"3175820431b80b0e6959bc49022a698a2baef0d7","tid":2509072,"uid":241384,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T08:00:32.000Z","msg":"1.收番租<br />\n2.英國有例寫到明一間屋最多住幾多人"},{"pid":"a876970e4c5b85d5cb9bb60d23f750d600b9b7c1","tid":2509072,"uid":255332,"like":1,"dislik